msgstr ""
"provider 'groq' 需要 API 密钥\n"
"\n"
"方式一：存储 API 密钥：\n"
"  lokit auth login --provider groq\n"
"\n"
"方式二：直接传递密钥：\n"
"  --api-key YOUR_KEY 或 export GROQ_API_KEY=YOUR_KEY\n"
"\n"
"免费获取 API 密钥： https://console.groq.com/keys"

